#1 Registration

SUM
Opening Home page and registration new user

STR
1 Open home page  via https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/
The following elements should be visible on the home page:
- Username input (for login)
- Password input (for login)
- Sign In button
- Username input (for registration)
- Email input (for registration)
- Password input (for registration)

2 Enter valid username into Username input field (example of valid username is..)
3 Enter valid email into Email input field (example of valid email: user@gmail.com)
4 Enter valid password in Password input field(example of valid password: there should be requirements for length(Password should be at least 12 characters) and characters in password)
5 Click on the Sign up for OurApp Button

EXP RES

1. Correct Username appears in right top corner
2. Create Post button displays
3. Sign Out button displays
4. Search icon displays
5. Chat icon displays
6. My Profile icon displays


#2 Login of an existing user

SUM
Opening Home page and login in the account of an existing user

STR

1 Open home page via https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/
The following elements should be visible on the home page:
- Username input (for login)
- Password input (for login)
- Sign In button
2 Enter valid username into Username input field
3 Enter valid password in Password input field
4 Click on the Sign in button

EXP RES
1. Correct Username appears in right top corner
2. Create Post button displays
3. Sign Out button displays
4. Search icon displays
5. Chat icon displays
6. My Profile icon displays

#3 Chat opening

SUM
Opening chat from user account

STR
1. Login to an EXISTING account using valid data (Username: goshia, Pass: 12345qwe!)
2. Click on 'Chat' icon

EXP RES
1. Chat window opens
2. 'Type a message' input field is displayed

#4 Post creating

SUM
Creating post in the system by user

STR

1. Login to an EXISTING account using valid data (Username: goshia, Pass: 12345qwe!).
2. Click on 'Create Post' button
3. Enter  text into title input (Test title text)
4. Enter  text into body content input: (Test title text)
5. Click on the  'Save New Post' button

EXP RES
1. Sign 'Test title text' is displayed
2. Sign 'Test title text' is displayed
3. Edit button is displayed
4. Delete button is displayed

#5 Sign out

SUM
Sign out user from profile

Precondition:
Login to an EXISTING account using valid data (Username: goshia, Pass: 12345qwe!)

STR
1 Click on the 'Sign Out' button

EXP RES

1 Home page opens(https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/)
The following elements should be visible on the home page:
